title: Lotus Botanicals
product_description: Ginger Root Dandruff-Control Shampoo with Tea Tree Oil 300 ml
product_details: {"description":"Ginger Root Dandruff-Control Shampoo with Tea Tree Oil"}
product_specifications:
[{"specification_name":"Concern","specification_value":"Dandruff"},{"specification_name":"Formulation","specification_value":"Liquid"},{"specification_name":"Hair Type","specification_value":"Normal"},{"specification_name":"How-to-Apply","specification_value":"
  • Gently massage into wet hair and scalp with fingertips to work into lather.
  • Rinse thoroughly.
"},{"specification_name":"Ingredients","specification_value":"Key Ingredients:
  • Ginger Root: For over 2500 years, ginger root has been used all over the world for its amazing hair benefits. With its antiseptic properties, it reduces scalp infections and dandruff. It also has conditioning properties that improve the look and feel of hair.
  • Tea Tree Oil: It clears the follicles and allows hair to breathe. Its antifungal nature prevents buildup of excess oil on the scalp.
Other Ingredients: Aqua, Caprylyl/capryl glucoside, sodium methyl cocoyl taurate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, PEG-150 Polyglyceryl-2 Tristearate (and) Laureth-3 (and) Dipropylene Glycol, Propanediol, Coco-Glucoside (and) Glyceryl Oleate, Glycerin, Coco diethanolamide, Climbazole, Polyquaternium-6, Panthenol, Zingiber Officinale (Ginger) Root Extract, Melaleuca Alternifolia (Tea Tree) Leaf Oil, Disodium EDTA, Caprylhydroxamic Acid (and) Phenethyl Alcohol, Fragrance."},{"specification_name":"Key Ingredient","specification_value":"Tea Tree"},{"specification_name":"Minimum Shelf Life in Months","specification_value":"36"},{"specification_name":"Minimum Usable Period in Months","specification_value":"36"},{"specification_name":"Preference","specification_value":"Paraben-Free"},{"specification_name":"Special Features","specification_value":"

product_description: Men ARC RACER All Purpose Sports Shoes
product_details: {"description":"A versatile all purpose sports shoe that can be used for running, fitness, or for casual wearRYDEFOAM midsole technology - an eTPU sole for best in class cushioning & energy returnAEROKNIT upper - a lightweight 3D Knit upper that is breathable & flexibleDiamond texture rubber outsole provides durability and tractionExternal heel counter & double loop lace system for extra stabilityWarranty: 3 monthsProduct StoryThe ARC RACER is made using the world's most innovative, comfortable and responsive sole material - eTPU (expanded thermoplastic polyurethane).Our proprietary RYDEFOAM technology is designed such that the shoe feels soft like a pillow on your feet while walking, yet springs into action the moment you need it to deliver on performance activities.Our world-class sole tech and 3D flexible knit is merged together by craftsmen with over 30 years of experience.The result is a shoe that can withstand the toughest of workouts while providing you all-day comfort and aesthetic versatility to wear to the office or for a night out.About ELEVARElevar is one of the fastest growing sports brands in India. It's able to do this by disrupting traditional market norms - by going direct-to-consumer, Elevar is able to cut out all middlemen and pass on savings to the customer.
